            correction: '$X_i \\sim \\mathcal{B}(p)$ (loi de Bernoulli de paramètre $p$).\n$$E(X_i) = \\boxed{p}$$\n$$V(X_i) = p(1-p) = \\boxed{p(1-p)}$$'
